headline: How Recent Developments Are Shaping the Otis Worldwide Investment Story
summary: Otis Worldwide has seen its Fair Value Estimate rise slightly from $99.23 to $100.23, reflecting a modest uptick in perceived intrinsic value. This comes as analysts adjust their assumptions. A higher discount rate indicates an elevated cost of capital, and slightly softer revenue growth forecasts are tempering the outlook. Stay tuned to see how evolving analyst perspectives could impact your understanding of Otis Worldwide’s investment potential in the months ahead. What Wall Street Has Been...
